---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us | A2Z Pest Control LLC" description="Family-owned and operated pest control in the Pittsburgh area since 1993. Serving Allegheny, Butler, and Washington Counties with dependable, discreet service.">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">About Us</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-story section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-layout">
        <div class="story-image reveal">
          <div class="story-frame">
            <img src="/images/unadjustednonraw_thumb_a1e1.jpg" alt="The A2Z Pest Control family" width="1706" height="2274" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="story-text reveal">
          <div class="story-year">
            <span class="year-number">1993</span>
            <span class="year-dash"></span>
            <span class="year-label">Present</span>
          </div>
          <h2>Family-owned. Pittsburgh-rooted.<br />Still at it after 30 years.</h2>
          <p>A2Z Pest Control LLC is a local, family-owned business. Since 1993, we've treated thousands of homes in Allegheny, Butler, and Washington Counties.</p>
          <p>As parents and pet owners, we understand what's essential in choosing a pest control company. At A2Z Pest Control, we treat your home like our own. Safety is our priority, letting you feel confident the work is done right.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="values-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="values-heading reveal">What Sets Us Apart</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-number">01</div>
          <h3>Unmarked Vehicles</h3>
          <p>We pull up in plain vehicles. Your pest problem is your business, not your neighborhood's.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-number">02</div>
          <h3>30+ Years</h3>
          <p>We've seen every pest problem Pittsburgh can throw at a home. There's no guesswork left for us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-number">03</div>
          <h3>No Pressure</h3>
          <p>We'll tell you what the problem is and what it costs. No scare tactics, no upselling treatments you don't need.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-number">04</div>
          <h3>On Time</h3>
          <p>When we say we'll be there, we're there. You have enough going on without rearranging your day for us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-number">05</div>
          <h3>Screened Staff</h3>
          <p>Background-checked, trained technicians who understand your home has kids and pets in it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-number">06</div>
          <h3>Free Estimates</h3>
          <p>Call, describe the issue, get a price. Most jobs don't need a site visit before we can quote.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="area-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="area-layout reveal">
        <div class="area-text">
          <h2>Service Area</h2>
          <p>We serve residential properties across three counties in the greater Pittsburgh region.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="area-list">
          <li class="area-item">
            <span class="area-county">Allegheny County</span>
          </li>
          <li class="area-item">
            <span class="area-county">Butler County</span>
          </li>
          <li class="area-item">
            <span class="area-county">Washington County</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-cta section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-block reveal">
        <h2>Ready to talk?</h2>
        <p>Give us a call during business hours. We pick up the phone and give you a straight answer.</p>
        <a href="tel:412-854-2224" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Call 412-854-2224</a>
        <p class="cta-hours">Monday through Friday, 8am to 3pm</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding-top: calc(80px + var(--space-xl));
    padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, oklch(0.12 0.02 155 / 0.3) 0%, var(--black) 100%);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 7rem);
  }

  /* ============ STORY ============ */
  .story-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.5fr 0.5fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .story-frame {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px oklch(0 0 0 / 0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);

    img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      object-fit: cover;
      aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    }
  }

  .story-year {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .year-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    color: var(--green);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .year-dash {
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--green-dim);
  }

  .year-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .story-text {
    h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    p {
      color: var(--text-dim);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .story-frame {
      max-width: 400px;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }
  }

  /* ============ VALUES ============ */
  .values-section {
    background: var(--dark);
    border-block: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .values-heading {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--black);
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: background 0.3s;
    position: relative;

    &:hover {
      background: oklch(0.1 0.02 155);

      .value-number {
        color: var(--green);
      }
    }
  }

  .value-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .value-card {
    h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    p {
      color: var(--text-dim);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 500px) {
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* ============ SERVICE AREA ============ */
  .area-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .area-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .area-text p {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .area-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .area-item {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--dark);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;

    &:hover {
      border-color: var(--green-dim);
      background: var(--green-glass);
    }
  }

  .area-county {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .area-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* ============ CTA ============ */
  .about-cta {
    text-align: center;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, oklch(0.15 0.04 155 / 0.3), transparent 60%),
      var(--black);
  }

  .cta-block {
    h2 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    }

    p {
      color: var(--text-dim);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }
  }

  .cta-hours {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 0.8rem !important;
    color: var(--text-faint) !important;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--black);

    &:hover {
      background: var(--green-bright);
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px oklch(0.72 0.19 155 / 0.3);
    }
  }

  .btn-lg {
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
</style>
